<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About -SANJAY</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/home.css">
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="nav-container">
            <a href="/" class="logo">JD SANJAY</a>
            <ul class="nav-menu">
                <li><a href="/" class="nav-link">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/about" class="nav-link">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="/projects" class="nav-link">Projects</a></li>
                <li><a href="/contact" class="nav-link">Contact</a></li>
                <li><a href="/add-project" class="nav-link">Add Project</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="content-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>About Me</h1>
            <div class="about-content">
                <p>I'm a passionate full-stack developer with 5+ years of experience in building web applications. I specialize in the MERN stack and have a strong foundation in modern JavaScript, React, Node.js, and MongoDB.</p>
                <p>When I'm not coding, you can find me contributing to open-source projects, writing technical blogs, or exploring new technologies. I'm always eager to learn and grow as a developer.</p>
                <div class="stats">
                    <div class="stat">
                        <h3>50+</h3>
                        <p>Projects</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat">
                        <h3>30+</h3>
                        <p>Clients</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat">
                        <h3>5+</h3>
                        <p>Years</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Sanjay. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

    <style>
        .content-section {
            min-height: calc(100vh - 200px);
            padding: 80px 20px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
        }

        .content-section h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0066ff, #ff0066);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .about-content p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #b0b9c1;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .stats {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stat h3 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #0066ff;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .stat p {
            color: #b0b9c1;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .stats {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</body>
</html>
